[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:basalt hidetitle=a | darkmode=a]]
[[module css]]
.footnotes-footer {
display:none;
}
.quote {
    background: #b8d4ff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    margin: 26px auto 0;
    max-width: 65%;
    min-height: 98px;
    padding: 24px;
    padding-top: 50px;
    position: relative;
    width: 65%;
}

.quote:before,
.quote:after {
    content: "";
    height: 98%;
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: -1;
}

.quote:before {
    background: #b3cffa;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    left: -5px;
    top: 4px;
    transform: rotate(-2.5deg);
}

.quote:after {
    background: #afcbf6;
    box-shadow: 0 0 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    right: -3px;
    top: 1px;
    transform: rotate(1.4deg);
}
[[/module]]

[[=]]
**"每天晚上的这个时候，他都在那里，望着星空。就好像，一定要看见什么似的。"**
[[/=]]

